      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Well-kept vehicle in good overall condition. It presents nicely inside and out, with a clean appearance and only the kind of light cosmetic wear you\u2019d expect from a properly used vehicle. Interior materials show normal age-related use but remain in good shape, and the vehicle should be a solid, dependable choice for someone looking for a clean driver without paying mint-condition money.",
