    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to sell, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation for the buyer who values affordability over frills. It shows its age and is best suited for someone looking for a practical project, a backup vehicle, or basic point-A-to-B use. If you want an accessible price and solid value for the money, this is a compelling opportunity.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap way to get on the road without spending a fortune? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, usable vehicle with plenty of life left for the right buyer. Great as a budget commuter, first car, or a handy little project if you enjoy tinkering. It has the kind of wear you\u2019d expect at this stage, but that also means no surprises about it being a showroom piece. If you want something straightforward, affordable, and full of potential, this could be a really solid fit.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Solid project or budget commuter with strong enthusiast appeal. The drivetrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis feels planted, and it has the kind of mechanical simplicity that makes it a great candidate for someone who wants a usable car with room to sort and improve. It shows its age cosmetically and will need attention consistent with a well-used vehicle, but it presents as complete and worthwhile rather than picked over. Great opportunity to get into an affordable driver/project platform at a realistic price.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap, honest driver. Not pretty, but it runs and gets the job done. Great budget buy. Priced to move.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is the kind of car that feels like it still has stories left to tell. A well-traveled machine with real character, it offers an honest, no-frills driving experience and the kind of practical potential that appeals to someone who sees value beyond first impressions. Whether you need an affordable runabout, a project with personality, or a dependable extra vehicle to keep life moving, this one brings rugged charm and purpose in equal measure. Priced to make sense and ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 5900.0,
